data.description: Extraordinary 6 bd (1 non-conforming)/4-bth craftsman home on 12.64-acres on sought-after South Hill. In the heart of the home, a chef's kitchen equipped w/massive island, GAS STOVE (CONNECTED TO GAS, RARE in acreage properties), dbl ovens, granite counters, & all Thermador appliances! Primary suite is a sanctuary, w/an ensuite bath, garden tub, walk-in shower, & a spacious walk-in closet. Marvelous basement boasts 1 bdrm w/Murphy bed, 1 bth w/walk-in shower & heated floors, capacious family room, wet bar (ideal for entertaining guests), & fingerprint locked storage for peace of mind. The convenience of a central vac system enhances the ease of cleaning. Includes GAS forced air, A/C, & cutting-edge Starlink System, ensuring reliable & high-speed internet. The expansive property offers endless opportunities for camping, sledding, hiking, wildlife, exploration, & ample room for a SHOP! 5 minutes away from all amenities on the South Hill! Ask your Realtor to see 3D Floorplan Virtual Tour & Amenities Handout!
